
<html lang="en">
    <%- include('./partials/header.ejs') %>
<body>

    <!-- Top Nav Bar -->
    <%- include('./partials/navbar.ejs') %>   




<!-- Main Content Section -->
<main id="donation-guidelines">
    
    <!-- Introduction -->
    <section class="content-section">
        <p>Proper preparation and care can make your blood donation experience smooth and positive. Follow these tips to ensure you are ready before, comfortable during, and well after your donation.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Before Donation -->
    <section class="content-section">
        <div class="contents" style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; gap: 3em;">

        <div class="photo">
        <h2>Before Donation</h2>
        <img src="images/food.jpg" alt="Before Donation Icon" class="stage-icon">
    </div>

    <div class="list">
        <ul>
            <li>Eat a healthy meal before you donate. Avoid fatty foods.</li>
            <li>Drink plenty of water before your appointment.</li>
            <li>Get a good night's sleep the night before.</li>
            <li>Avoid alcohol and caffeine on the day of donation.</li>
            <li>Wear a shirt with sleeves that can be rolled up.</li>
            <li>Bring your ID and any donor card if you have one.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
    </section>

    <!-- During Donation -->
    <section class="content-section">
        <div class="contents" style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; gap: 3em;">
       

        <div class="photo">
        <h2>During Donation</h2>
        <img src="images/breath.jpg" alt="During Donation Icon" class="stage-icon">
        </div>

        <div class="list">
        <ul>
            <li>Relax and take deep breaths. Stay calm.</li>
            <li>Inform the staff if you feel uncomfortable or unwell.</li>
            <li>Squeeze the stress ball provided to help the blood flow.</li>
            <li>Enjoy the snacks and refreshments offered after donation.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    </div>

    </section>

    <!-- After Donation -->
    <section class="content-section">
        <div class="contents" style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; gap: 3em;">
       
        <div class="photo">
        <h2>After Donation</h2>
        <img src="./images/drinkingwater.png" alt="After Donation Icon" class="stage-icon">
        </div>

        <div class="list">
        <ul>
            <li>Drink plenty of fluids to stay hydrated.</li>
            <li>Avoid strenuous activities for at least 24 hours.</li>
            <li>Keep the bandage on for a few hours and avoid using that arm heavily.</li>
            <li>Eat a healthy meal with iron-rich foods to replenish your body.</li>
            <li>If you feel lightheaded or dizzy, sit or lie down until you feel better.</li>
            <li>Remember, you can donate again in 8 weeks (56 days).</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <section class="content-section">
        <h2>Ready to Donate?</h2>
        <p>Follow these tips to ensure a successful donation experience. If you have any questions or concerns, don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
        <a href="/appointment" class="cta-button">Schedule an Appointment</a>
    </section>

</main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>   
    
</body>
</html>